import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { map } from 'rxjs'; // import '../../../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'; // import '../../../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.js'; let checkedArray: any[] = []; let mapper= new Map(); mapper.set("id_blore","Bangalore"); mapper.set("id_hyd","Hyderabad"); mapper.set("id_kol","Kolkata"); @Component({ selector: 'app-nav-bar', templateUrl: './nav-bar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./nav-bar.component.css'] }) export class NavBarComponent { onChange(event:any){ let element=event.target; let eid=element.id; // alert(eid); if(element.checked && !checkedArray.includes(mapper.get(eid))){ console.log("it is checked"); checkedArray.push(mapper.get(eid)); } else if(!element.checked){ console.log("unchecked"); if(mapper.get(eid in checkedArray) { for (let i = 0; i < checkedArray.length; i++) { console.log(mapper.get(eid)); if (checkedArray[i] == mapper.get(eid)) { console.log("deleting"); checkedArray.splice(i,1); } } } } console.log(checkedArray); } }
